        <abstract> 
<p>Sends, as corroboration of earlier articles on hedgehogs carrying fruit on their spines, a passage from a letter from R. Swinhoe [<hi rend="doubleUnderline">5598</hi>] describing hedgehogs carrying strawberries to their holes.</p> 
